<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.831722>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Decoralampra fulgencioi gen. et. sp. nov.: Habitus, (A) dorsal and (B) ventral; (C) head; (D) right tegmina, dorsal view (Sc: subcosta vein; CuP: Cubitus posterior vein); (E) prothoracic leg, anterior view; (F) hind basitarsomere, ventral view; (G) supraanal plate, ventral view; (H) male subgenital plate and genital phallomeres, dorsal view (fs: folded structure; L 3: hook-like phallomere; L 2 d: median phallomere; R 1 – R 5: sclerites of R phallomere)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/831722/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

